snippet.title: Pro Yakyuu Spirits 5 Kanzenban (PS2) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Happy Fourth of July! This is a full game of Pro Yakyuu Spirits 5 Kanzenban (Perfect Complete Edition), a baseball video game by Konami, released December 2008. It's an updated roster version basically, including some minor stadium renovation and new uniform changes also. 

This is the PlayStation 2 version, and the game was also released on PS3.
